 237                         {

 596             {
 597                 attributes->Accept(*this);
 598                 formatter.WriteLine();
 599             }
 600             if (memberFunctionNode.GetSpecifiers() != Specifiers.none)
 601             {
 602                 formatter.Write(SpecifierStr(memberFunctionNode.GetSpecifiers()));
 603                 formatter.Write(" ");
 604             }
 605             memberFunctionNode.ReturnTypeExpr()->Accept(*this);
 606             formatter.Write(" ");
 607             formatter.Write(ToUtf8(memberFunctionNode.GroupId()));
 608             formatter.Write("(");
 609             int np = memberFunctionNode.Parameters().Count();
 610             for (int i = 0; i < np; ++i;)
 611             {
 612                 if (i > 0)
 613                 {
 614                     formatter.Write(", ");
 615                 }
 616                 memberFunctionNode.Parameters()[i]->Accept(*this);
 617             }
 618             formatter.Write(")");
 619             if (memberFunctionNode.IsConst())
 620             {
 621                 formatter.Write(" const");
 622             }
 623             if ((memberFunctionNode.WhereConstraint() != null))
 624             {
 625                 formatter.WriteLine();
 626                 formatter.IncIndent();
 627                 memberFunctionNode.WhereConstraint()->Accept(*this);
 628                 formatter.DecIndent();
 629             }
 630             if ((memberFunctionNode.Body() != null))
 631             {
 632                 formatter.WriteLine();
 633                 memberFunctionNode.Body()->Accept(*this);
 634             }
 635             else
 636             {
 637                 formatter.WriteLine(";");
 638             }
 639         }

 938         public override void Visit(ConceptNode& conceptNode)
 939         {
 940             WriteEmptyLine();
 941             if (conceptNode.GetSpecifiers() != Specifiers.none)
 942             {
 943                 formatter.Write(SpecifierStr(conceptNode.GetSpecifiers()));
 944                 formatter.Write(" ");
 945             }
 946             formatter.Write("concept ");
 947             conceptNode.Id()->Accept(*this);
 948             formatter.Write("<");
 949             int n = conceptNode.TypeParameters().Count();
 950             for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i;)
 951             {
 952                 if (i > 0)
 953                 {
 954                     formatter.Write(", ");
 955                 }
 956                 conceptNode.TypeParameters()[i]->Accept(*this);
 957             }
 958             formatter.Write(">");
 959             if ((conceptNode.Refinement() != null))
 960             {
 961                 conceptNode.Refinement()->Accept(*this);
 962             }
 963             formatter.WriteLine();
 964             int nc = conceptNode.Constraints().Count();
 965             for (int i = 0; i < nc; ++i;)
 966             {
 967                 ConstraintNode* constraintNode = conceptNode.Constraints()[i];
 968                 if (constraintNode->IsHeaderConstraint())
 969                 {
 970                     formatter.IncIndent();
 971                     constraintNode->Accept(*this);
 972                     formatter.DecIndent();
 973                     formatter.WriteLine();
 974                 }
 975             }
 976             formatter.WriteLine("{");
 977             formatter.IncIndent();
 978             for (int i = 0; i < nc; ++i;)
 979             {
 980                 ConstraintNode* constraintNode = conceptNode.Constraints()[i];
 981                 if (constraintNode->IsHeaderConstraint()) continue;
 982                 constraintNode->Accept(*this);
 983             }
 984             int na = conceptNode.Axioms().Count();
 985             for (int i = 0; i < na; ++i;)
 986             {
 987                 conceptNode.Axioms()[i]->Accept(*this);
 988             }
 989             formatter.DecIndent();
 990             formatter.WriteLine("}");
 991             emptyLine = true;
 992         }

1761         public override void Visit(CastNode& castNode)
1762         {
1763             formatter.Write("cast<");
1764             castNode.TargetTypeExpr()->Accept(*this);
1765             formatter.Write(">(");
1766             castNode.SourceExpr()->Accept(*this);
1767             formatter.Write(")");
1768         }
1769         public override void Visit(ConstructNode& constructNode)
1770         {
1771             formatter.Write("construct<");
1772             constructNode.TypeExpr()->Accept(*this);
1773             formatter.Write(">(");
1774             int n = constructNode.Arguments().Count();
1775             for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i;)
1776             {
1777                 if (i > 0)
1778                 {
1779                     formatter.Write(", ");
1780                 }
1781                 constructNode.Arguments()[i]->Accept(*this);
1782             }
1783             formatter.Write(")");
1784         }
1785         public override void Visit(NewNode& newNode)
1786         {
1787             formatter.Write("new ");
1788             newNode.TypeExpr()->Accept(*this);
1789             formatter.Write("(");
1790             int n = newNode.Arguments().Count();
1791             for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i;)
1792             {
1793                 if (i > 0)
1794                 {
1795                     formatter.Write(", ");
1796                 }
1797                 newNode.Arguments()[i]->Accept(*this);
1798             }
1799             formatter.Write(")");
1800         }
1801         public override void Visit(ThisNode& thisNode)
1802         {
1803             formatter.Write("this");
1804         }
1805         public override void Visit(BaseNode& baseNode)
1806         {
1807             formatter.Write("base");
1808         }
1809         public override void Visit(ParenthesizedExpressionNode& parenthesizedExpressionNode)
1810         {
1811             formatter.Write("(");
1812             parenthesizedExpressionNode.Subject()->Accept(*this);
1813             formatter.Write(")");
1814         }
1815         public override void Visit(GlobalVariableNode& globalVariableNode)
1816         {
1817             WriteEmptyLine();
1818             if (globalVariableNode.GetSpecifiers() != Specifiers.none)
1819             {
1820                 formatter.Write(SpecifierStr(globalVariableNode.GetSpecifiers()));
1821                 formatter.Write(" ");
1822             }
1823             globalVariableNode.TypeExpr()->Accept(*this);
1824             formatter.Write(" ");
1825             globalVariableNode.Id()->Accept(*this);
1826             if ((globalVariableNode.Initializer() != null))
1827             {
1828                 formatter.Write(" = ");
1829                 globalVariableNode.Initializer()->Accept(*this);
1830             }
1831             formatter.WriteLine(";");
1832             emptyLine = true;
1833         }
1834         public override void Visit(AttributeNode& attribute)
1835         {
1836             formatter.Write(ToUtf8(attribute.Name()));
1837             if (!attribute.Value().IsEmpty())
1838             {
1839                 formatter.Write("=");
1840                 formatter.Write("\"" + StringStr(ToUtf8(attribute.Value())) + "\"");
1841             }
1842         }
1843         public override void Visit(AttributesNode& attributes)
1844         {
1845             formatter.Write("[");
1846             int n = cast<int>(attributes.GetAttributes().Count());
1847             for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i;)
1848             {
1849                 if (i > 0)
1850                 {
1851                     formatter.Write(", ");
1852                 }
1853                 attributes.GetAttributes()[i]->Accept(*this);
1854             }
1855             formatter.Write("]");
1856         }
1857         public override void Visit(CommentNode& comment)
1858         {
1859             formatter.WriteLine("// " + ToUtf8(comment.Comment()));
1860             formatter.WriteLine();
1861         }
1862         private void WriteEmptyLine()
1863         {
1864             if (emptyLine)
1865             {
1866                 formatter.WriteLine();
1867                 emptyLine = false;
1868             }
1869         }
1870         private CodeFormatter& formatter;
1871         private bool omitNewLine;
1872         private bool omitSemicolon;
1873         private bool emptyLine;
1874     }
1875 } // namespace Cm.Ast
